Title: 'Tough But Enjoying Journey of My Summer Hike '
DateModified: '2019-02-12'
DatePublished: '2019-02-12'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/tough-but-enjoying-journey-of-my-summer-hike
SetInCountry: Pakistan
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Aqib Shafiq
AuthorCountry: Pakistan
Text: 'It is Story of My Last year Summer Hike .Being a member of Pakistan Scout Association
  at my home university I got a chance to participate in Annual Summer hiking and
  tracking course it is ten days Course .Before this I don''t have any experience
  about Hiking so it is very tough for me complete the challenging Path of Northern
  area of Pakistan but With courgette and Passion I complete the Course and Find One
  thing on myself and that is I can do anything with courge and Passion

  Active social worker, community development contributor, traveller and other than
  that I always like to take the responsibility and lead. I am associated with Agriversity
  Scout group as a rover and also working as a volunteer with Agri tourism society
  and IBA NTHP. I like solving problems and leading people. All of this has enabled
  me to pave a way for the people from my hometown to look for better opportunities
  and how to avail them. I am excited and looking forward to serving the community,
  I hope that we can bring a positive change'
